channel.title: Comments on: Better than OK Computer?

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: Hahahaha. I can't fathom what that writer was thinking. It's not a bad record, but it ain't no OK Computer. That's just blasphemy.

item.description: the stuff i've heard doesn't even touch pablo honey. so i'm calling this a long shot.
